	quests: [
		{
			description: [
				"Welcome to the start of your zoo. Great things come from humble beginnings."
				""
				"You may have already noticed a lot of critters wandering around. You should start building exhibits to put them on display. Your zoo will be essential to the funding of your research."
				""
				"Keep in mind that there are many mods an animal might come from, and this will affect its behavior and needs. Some will need to be fed and entertained after they are tamed. But if you keep them happy, they will reward you."
				""
				"[ \"You may want to start down the \", { \"text\": \"Path of the Owl\", \"underlined\": \"true\", \"clickEvent\": { \"action\": \"change_page\", \"value\": \"51893424D161C6E7\" } }, \"; this will make it much easier to tell exactly what kind of animal you are dealing\" ] with."
			]
			id: "77ABAB18A01650BA"
			rewards: [
