		{
			dependencies: ["77ABAB18A01650BA"]
			description: [
				"The Zoojoyizer is the key to converting abstract happiness into cold hard material goods. Put one at the center of an exhibit with a sample of the animal's dna and it will generate resources for you every morning. The items created depend on the animal and how well decorated the exhibit is."
				""
				"You can look in JEI to see what animals make what resources, and what they like in their environment."
			]
			id: "2044B4978E27AE26"
