		{
			dependencies: ["77ABAB18A01650BA"]
			description: [
				"Ambient, tiny, and small animals from the ZAWA mod can be picked up by right clicking them with an empty hand. Animals can then be set down by sneaking. Practice by catching these &aButterflies&r."
				""
				"It is recommended that you start your exhibit with these sorts of small animals. Animals that struggle while you hold them are best carried with a &9handling glove&r in your offhand."
				""
				"[ \"More advanced capture methods can be unlocked by pursuing the \", { \"text\": \"Path of the Spider\", \"underlined\": \"true\", \"clickEvent\": { \"action\": \"change_page\", \"value\": \"000F0C223F4007A3\" } }, \".\" ]"
