		{
			dependencies: ["32B6A25A9A456DEB"]
			description: [
				"Smaller \"ambient\" animals like these &aButterflies&r are simple to care for; they have no ongoing needs. But more complex animals will need food and water and even enrichment in their environments in order to stay healthy and in good breeding condition."
				""
				"After breeding some additional butterflies for food, try out this &aTree Frog&r next. It is still small enough to catch by hand, but will require care once it has been tamed with &9insecitivore kibble&r."
